No. D-2564. In the Matter of Discipline of Sandra L. Craig. 562 U.S. 817, 131 S. Ct. 410,

178 L. Ed. 2d 274,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7506. October 4, 2010.

Sandra L. Craig, of Pacific, Missouri, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why she should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
